title: NFL teams ranked by their franchise QBs & Warriors vs Bulls dynasty
itunes:title: NFL teams ranked by their franchise QBs & Warriors vs Bulls dynasty
description:
Dave Dameshek is joined in Studio 66 by Cole Wright and Ali Bhanpuri who makes his first appearance on the DDFP! Before getting into the big topic of the show, everyone celebrated Dave's birthday - who also shares it with Joe Montana and Vince Lombardi (1:02)! Then, the trio got into Ali's NFL.com article on ranking NFL teams based on their franchise quarterbacks (8:10). Next, Shek, Cole and Ali spoke about Kevin Durant's unfortunate injury during the NBA Finals and which dynasty was better between the current Golden State Warriors or the 90s Chicago Bulls (37:25)? The guys round out the show by debating if pitchers are allowed to complain about batters who celebrate home runs (55:15)?
